rawContent:
Depression, a
serpent eating its
own tail while
wrapped around the
neck of
the afflicted.
Purple skin is
clawed by the
untrimmed nails of
distorted time.
The catharsis of
weeping is
interrupted by
life's disdain.
Tears at a
standstill, as are
the veins.

#poetry #depression
